# Pulsate EMS

Pulsate EMS is a modern Electronic Patient Report Form (ePRF) and Ambulance Management System developed for Pulsate Emergency Medical Services.

## Features

- Secure User Login
- Electronic Patient Report Forms (ePRF)
- Declaration of Death Forms
- Patient Refusal Forms
- Interfacility Transfer Forms
- Patient Search
- Digital Signatures
- PDF Generation
- Fleet Management
- Staff Management
- Drug Register
- Equipment Checklists
- Reporting Dashboard

## Technology Stack

### Frontend
- React
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS

### Backend
- Node.js
- Express

### Database
- PostgreSQL
- Prisma ORM

### Authentication
- JWT

